	<value_smv>Bệnh gia súc - gia cầm</value_smv>
	</item></technicalAssistance_o>
	<diseaseContent_html>&lt;p style="margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; font-family: 'Open Sans', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: Open Sans, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14px;"&gt;KH&amp;Aacute;I NIỆM&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; font-family: 'Open Sans', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: Open Sans, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14px;"&gt;Bệnh do vi khuẩn E.coli khi ph&amp;aacute;t triển trong ruột heo sinh ra c&amp;aacute;c ngoại độc tố v&amp;agrave; c&amp;aacute;c chất n&amp;agrave;y thấm v&amp;agrave;o m&amp;aacute;u đầu độc cơ thể&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; font-family: 'Open Sans', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: Open Sans, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14px;"&gt;Vai tr&amp;ograve; vi khuẩn E.coli l&amp;agrave; kế ph&amp;aacute;t, cần c&amp;oacute; th&amp;ecirc;m c&amp;aacute;c yếu tố thuận lợi ti&amp;ecirc;n ph&amp;aacute;t: chuồng bẩn lạnh; kh&amp;ocirc;ng kiểm so&amp;aacute;t được lượng &amp;amp; chất của thức ăn.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; font-family: 'Open Sans', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: Open Sans, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14px;"&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; font-family: 'Open Sans', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: Open Sans, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14px;"&gt;DẤU HIỆU BỆNH L&amp;Yacute;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; font-family: 'Open Sans', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: Open Sans, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14px;"&gt;Bệnh thường ph&amp;aacute;t sinh tr&amp;ecirc;n heo trong khoảng 25 &amp;ndash; 50kg v&amp;agrave; tr&amp;ecirc;n những heo b&amp;eacute;o tốt; Hai dấu hiệu ch&amp;iacute;nh của heo bệnh l&amp;agrave; ph&amp;ugrave; thủng v&amp;agrave; rối loạn vận động&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; font-family: 'Open Sans', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: Open Sans, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14px;"&gt;- Ph&amp;ugrave;: thấy r&amp;otilde; ở v&amp;ugrave;ng quanh mắt, v&amp;ugrave;ng tr&amp;aacute;n&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; font-family: 'Open Sans', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: Open Sans, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14px;"&gt;- Rối loạn vận động: heo bị co giật hay bại liệt 2 ch&amp;acirc;n sau.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; font-family: 'Open Sans', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: Open Sans, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14px;"&gt;Mổ kh&amp;aacute;m heo bệnh sẽ thấy:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; font-family: 'Open Sans', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: Open Sans, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14px;"&gt;- T&amp;iacute;ch nhiều dịch trong xoang ngực, xoang bụng&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; font-family: 'Open Sans', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: Open Sans, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14px;"&gt;- Ph&amp;ugrave; thủng m&amp;agrave;ng treo ruột, Vi&amp;ecirc;m phổi kẻ&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; font-family: 'Open Sans', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff;"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; font-family: 'Open Sans', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: Open Sans, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14px;"&gt;BIỆN PH&amp;Aacute;P GIẢI QUYẾT&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; font-family: 'Open Sans', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: Open Sans, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14px;"&gt;T&amp;aacute;ch ri&amp;ecirc;ng heo bệnh. Tập trung chăm s&amp;oacute;c những heo chưa bệnh, nếu to&amp;agrave;n trại c&amp;agrave;ng tốt (đ&amp;acirc;y l&amp;agrave; điểm mấu chốt)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; font-family: 'Open Sans', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: Open Sans, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14px;"&gt;* Với heo chưa bệnh:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; font-family: 'Open Sans', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: Open Sans, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14px;"&gt;- Giảm lượng thức ăn c&amp;ograve;n 2/3, cho thức ăn dễ ti&amp;ecirc;u (như th&amp;ecirc;m ch&amp;aacute;o); kh&amp;ocirc;ng cho ăn sau 17h. Khi t&amp;igrave;nh h&amp;igrave;nh bệnh giảm sẽ tăng dần lượng thức ăn trở lại. Heo sau 60kg/con sẽ cho ăn tự do&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; font-family: 'Open Sans', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: Open Sans, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14px;"&gt;- Acid h&amp;oacute;a thức ăn với ACID MIXED (pha nước cho uống), cho th&amp;ecirc;m probiotic như BIO ACIMIN Gold (trộn v&amp;agrave;o thức ăn). Cho d&amp;ugrave;ng li&amp;ecirc;n tục &amp;iacute;t nhất 10 ng&amp;agrave;y&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; font-family: 'Open Sans', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: Open Sans, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14px;"&gt;- Tăng cường chuyển h&amp;oacute;a với MEKOSAL (ti&amp;ecirc;m mỗi tuần/ lần); ti&amp;ecirc;m ngay mỗi con heo 1 liều VITAMIN ADE (2 th&amp;aacute;ng sau ti&amp;ecirc;m lại)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; font-family: 'Open Sans', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: Open Sans, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14px;"&gt;- D&amp;ugrave;ng BYE-CILOX + APRA-COLIS trộn v&amp;agrave;o thức ăn li&amp;ecirc;n tuc &amp;iacute;t nhất 10 ng&amp;agrave;y&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; font-family: 'Open Sans', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: Open Sans, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14px;"&gt;- Ti&amp;ecirc;m ngay cho mỗi con 1 liều CL- AMOXGEN (chỉ cần 1 lần)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; font-family: 'Open Sans', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: Open Sans, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14px;"&gt;- Sau khi can thiệp khoảng 5 ng&amp;agrave;y, d&amp;ugrave;ng VIMILAC PLUS 2 (trộn thức ăn &amp;iacute;t nhất 5 ng&amp;agrave;y), rồi sau đ&amp;oacute; d&amp;ugrave;ng MKV- GROWTH NEW trộn v&amp;agrave;o thức ăn&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; font-family: 'Open Sans', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: Open Sans, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14px;"&gt;* Với heo đang bệnh: rất kh&amp;oacute; chữa trị&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; font-family: 'Open Sans', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: Open Sans, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14px;"&gt;- Ti&amp;ecirc;m ngay 1 liều TROFURIT&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; font-family: 'Open Sans', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: Open Sans, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14px;"&gt;- 2h sau ti&amp;ecirc;m th&amp;ecirc;m 1 liều TROFURIT + 1 liều HEPTAMINOL (hay cafein) + 1 liều DEXASONE&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; font-family: 'Open Sans', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: Open Sans, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14px;"&gt;- 2h sau ti&amp;ecirc;m 1 liều CATAXIM (hay CL-AMOXGEN)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; font-family: 'Open Sans', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: Open Sans, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14px;"&gt;- Mỗi ng&amp;agrave;y ti&amp;ecirc;m 1 liều CL-AMOXGEN (&amp;iacute;t nhất 3 ng&amp;agrave;y), 1 liều CAFEIN, cho uống th&amp;ecirc;m SORBITOL&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; font-family: 'Open Sans', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: Open Sans, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14px;"&gt;- Cho heo bệnh ăn uống như heo chưa bệnh&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; font-family: 'Open Sans', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: Open Sans, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14px;"&gt;* Với chuồng trại:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; font-family: 'Open Sans', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: Open Sans, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14px;"&gt;- Cần giữ kh&amp;ocirc;, ấm, sạch. Tuyệt đối kh&amp;ocirc;ng cho g&amp;agrave;, vịt, ch&amp;oacute; v&amp;agrave;o chuồng heo&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; font-family: 'Open Sans', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: Open Sans, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14px;"&gt;- S&amp;aacute;t tr&amp;ugrave;ng chuồng ng&amp;agrave;y 1 lần&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; font-family: 'Open Sans', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: Open Sans, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14px;"&gt;* Ph&amp;ograve;ng bệnh:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; font-family: 'Open Sans', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: Open Sans, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14px;"&gt;- Heo từ 20 đến 50kg/con n&amp;ecirc;n cho ăn định lượng kết hợp d&amp;ugrave;ng c&amp;aacute;c chất acidifier, probiotic&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; font-family: 'Open Sans', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: Open Sans, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14px;"&gt;- Bố tr&amp;iacute; đủ m&amp;aacute;ng ăn&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; font-family: 'Open Sans', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: Open Sans, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14px;"&gt;- Khi c&amp;oacute; stress hay khi nghi ngờ n&amp;ecirc;n d&amp;ugrave;ng APRA-COLIS trộn v&amp;agrave;o thức ăn &amp;iacute;t nhất 3 ng&amp;agrave;y.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</diseaseContent_html>
